Dialogue: 0,0:00:33.70,0:00:36.24,Default,,0,0,0,,Can you imagine...
Dialogue: 0,0:00:36.24,0:00:41.45,Default,,0,0,0,,...a life in which you could never\Ntouch the one you love?
Dialogue: 0,0:00:41.45,0:00:44.33,Default,,0,0,0,,He takes the life of whatever he touches.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:44.33,0:00:47.79,Default,,0,0,0,,That was the curse the witch put on him.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:47.79,0:00:52.09,Default,,0,0,0,,Plants, animals... and people\Nare no exception, of course.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:52.09,0:00:55.47,Default,,0,0,0,,Regarding her son, doomed to live his life\Nwithout knowing the warmth of another,
Dialogue: 0,0:00:55.47,0:00:58.18,Default,,0,0,0,,his mother only complained.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:58.18,0:01:00.68,Default,,0,0,0,,"That child is like Death incarnate..."
Dialogue: 0,0:01:00.68,0:01:01.68,Default,,0,0,0,,she said.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:05.35,0:01:08.69,Default,,0,0,0,,You're getting too close to me\Nagain today, Alice! Way too close!
Dialogue: 0,0:01:08.69,0:01:11.40,Default,,0,0,0,,Your reactions are so adorable,\NYour Grace,
Dialogue: 0,0:01:11.40,0:01:13.94,Default,,0,0,0,,I can't help wanting to see them up close.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:13.94,0:01:15.99,Default,,0,0,0,,Okay then, take this!
Dialogue: 0,0:01:15.99,0:01:18.62,Default,,0,0,0,,I won't get self-conscious\Nif I can't see you!
Dialogue: 0,0:01:18.62,0:01:21.66,Default,,0,0,0,,You truly are adorable, Your Grace.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:21.66,0:01:23.41,Default,,0,0,0,,My ears are totally defenseless!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:54.88,0:02:59.68,Default,,0,0,0,,{\an8}"Episode 2: The Duke, His Butler,\Nand a Lost Cat"
Dialogue: 0,0:02:54.88,0:02:59.68,Default,,0,0,0,,Please forgive me for my extended absence.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:59.68,0:03:02.51,Default,,0,0,0,,I have fully recovered\Nfrom my back injury,
Dialogue: 0,0:03:02.51,0:03:05.68,Default,,0,0,0,,so I shall be returning\Nto work as of today.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:05.68,0:03:08.52,Default,,0,0,0,,That's wonderful.\NGood to have you back, Rob.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:08.52,0:03:11.27,Default,,0,0,0,,I imagine I caused you\Nsome trouble as well, Alice.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:11.27,0:03:14.48,Default,,0,0,0,,I left the care of His Grace\Nentirely in your hands.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:14.48,0:03:16.65,Default,,0,0,0,,You needn't worry about me.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:16.65,0:03:19.65,Default,,0,0,0,,I was able to spend the night\Ntogether with His Grace, so...
Dialogue: 0,0:03:19.65,0:03:22.20,Default,,0,0,0,,Stop saying things that\Ncould be misconstrued!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:22.20,0:03:25.83,Default,,0,0,0,,Seeing you two always\Nputs a smile on my face.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:25.83,0:03:28.41,Default,,0,0,0,,You need to keep your subordinate\Nfrom sexually harassing me!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:31.29,0:03:34.50,Default,,0,0,0,,And now, I shall take my leave.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:37.30,0:03:39.13,Default,,0,0,0,,It's the morning after Rob got back,
Dialogue: 0,0:03:39.13,0:03:42.89,Default,,0,0,0,,and it looks like he's already\Nhard at work around the estate.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:42.89,0:03:46.56,Default,,0,0,0,,Yes, even doing the jobs that\Nare too much for me to handle.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:46.56,0:03:48.47,Default,,0,0,0,,He's superhuman. That's why.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:50.77,0:03:54.48,Default,,0,0,0,,Rob's been a butler to me from the\Ntime I lived at my family's residence.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:54.48,0:03:57.94,Default,,0,0,0,,He was also the only one\Nto come with me to this estate.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:57.94,0:04:00.53,Default,,0,0,0,,You could say he was like a father to me.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:04.78,0:04:08.24,Default,,0,0,0,,So, how long do you plan\Non standing there?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:08.24,0:04:12.04,Default,,0,0,0,,Rob has taken all the work\NI would normally do.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:12.04,0:04:14.96,Default,,0,0,0,,Does my presence here bother you?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:14.96,0:04:17.42,Default,,0,0,0,,Well, it's just that I can't\Nconcentrate on my reading...
Dialogue: 0,0:04:19.09,0:04:22.67,Default,,0,0,0,,I hope I'm not disturbing you.\NI've brought you your tea.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:22.67,0:04:24.64,Default,,0,0,0,,But he was just in the yard a moment ago!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:27.55,0:04:30.35,Default,,0,0,0,,Aren't you working a bit too hard, Rob?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:30.35,0:04:31.48,Default,,0,0,0,,Who, me?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:31.48,0:04:34.27,Default,,0,0,0,,Well, you are sort of on the mend and all.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:34.27,0:04:36.94,Default,,0,0,0,,Why don't you let Alice\Ndo some of the work, too?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:36.94,0:04:40.15,Default,,0,0,0,,How kind of you to worry.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:40.15,0:04:44.70,Default,,0,0,0,,I may have been a bit too eager to get\Nback to work after my absence, but...
Dialogue: 0,0:04:44.70,0:04:48.08,Default,,0,0,0,,...you needn't worry about me, Your Grace.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:48.08,0:04:51.50,Default,,0,0,0,,Very well. We'll divide the cleaning to be\Ndone around the estate and get to work.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:51.50,0:04:53.71,Default,,0,0,0,,Let's go, Alice.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:53.71,0:04:54.71,Default,,0,0,0,,All right.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:02.09,0:05:03.72,Default,,0,0,0,,What is with her?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:05.09,0:05:07.18,Default,,0,0,0,,This is really good!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:07.18,0:05:11.27,Default,,0,0,0,,Rob's work hasn't\Nsuffered any, to be sure.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:11.27,0:05:14.39,Default,,0,0,0,,It may be boorish of me to worry.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:14.39,0:05:15.31,Default,,0,0,0,,Still...
Dialogue: 0,0:05:15.31,0:05:16.48,Default,,0,0,0,,Alice?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:17.48,0:05:20.02,Default,,0,0,0,,There's something I wanted to ask you...
Dialogue: 0,0:05:21.86,0:05:24.24,Default,,0,0,0,,I-It's me! What the heck\Nare you doing, Rob?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:24.24,0:05:26.20,Default,,0,0,0,,Oh, it's you, Your Grace.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:26.20,0:05:30.28,Default,,0,0,0,,Forgive me. My eyes have been blurry\Nlately, and it makes things hard to see.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:30.28,0:05:32.41,Default,,0,0,0,,That's a sign of aging eyes!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:32.41,0:05:34.08,Default,,0,0,0,,I've told you before, haven't I?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:34.08,0:05:36.58,Default,,0,0,0,,That lately, the effects of your\Nold age have gotten a bit worse.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:36.58,0:05:38.42,Default,,0,0,0,,If you touch me, you'll die.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:38.42,0:05:40.96,Default,,0,0,0,,That doesn't mean I want\Nyou to avoid me, but...
Dialogue: 0,0:05:40.96,0:05:43.67,Default,,0,0,0,,...you have to look out\Nfor yourself a bit more.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:43.67,0:05:45.30,Default,,0,0,0,,And you're hard of hearing, too!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:45.30,0:05:46.72,Default,,0,0,0,,What's the matter?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:46.72,0:05:50.35,Default,,0,0,0,,Oh, Alice, it's you.\NCan you talk some sense into him?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:50.35,0:05:51.60,Default,,0,0,0,,Pardon me.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:57.39,0:06:00.31,Default,,0,0,0,,This is the real Alice, right?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:00.31,0:06:03.07,Default,,0,0,0,,It's Alice! She's the only\Nother person around here!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:03.07,0:06:06.36,Default,,0,0,0,,I don't get it.\NYour work is flawless, and yet...
Dialogue: 0,0:06:08.11,0:06:13.49,Default,,0,0,0,,When you've been a butler for as long as\NI have, your body remembers the work.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:13.49,0:06:16.29,Default,,0,0,0,,So, you needn't worry about me.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:16.29,0:06:20.83,Default,,0,0,0,,I shall serve you for as long\Nas I live, Your Grace.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:23.00,0:06:24.00,Default,,0,0,0,,Rob...
Dialogue: 0,0:06:25.55,0:06:27.05,Default,,0,0,0,,Is it your back again?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:27.05,0:06:28.93,Default,,0,0,0,,So it seems...
Dialogue: 0,0:06:45.40,0:06:48.07,Default,,0,0,0,,All right. This is sounding good.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:48.07,0:06:51.41,Default,,0,0,0,,In case my family decides to disown\Nme somewhere down the road,
Dialogue: 0,0:06:51.41,0:06:56.37,Default,,0,0,0,,I've been writing a bunch of songs\Nso I can make a living with my music.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:56.37,0:06:59.41,Default,,0,0,0,,For as long as I can remember,\Nthe only thing I ever got praised for...
Dialogue: 0,0:06:59.41,0:07:01.88,Default,,0,0,0,,...was my piano playing.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:01.88,0:07:05.17,Default,,0,0,0,,Having still not found any way\Nof breaking the witch's curse,
Dialogue: 0,0:07:05.17,0:07:09.80,Default,,0,0,0,,playing the piano is my dream\Nas well as my only hope.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:09.80,0:07:11.34,Default,,0,0,0,,Is that a requiem?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:12.34,0:07:17.52,Default,,0,0,0,,Forgive me. While I was cleaning, I heard\Nthis beautiful song being played, and...
Dialogue: 0,0:07:17.52,0:07:20.94,Default,,0,0,0,,In that case, could you come up and\Nspeak to me more like a normal person?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:20.94,0:07:22.56,Default,,0,0,0,,What do you mean by "normal"?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:22.56,0:07:24.82,Default,,0,0,0,,I mean, "Don't lean in so close to me"!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:24.82,0:07:26.36,Default,,0,0,0,,Don't bug me, okay?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:26.36,0:07:29.53,Default,,0,0,0,,Rob is resting, so just do your own work.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:29.53,0:07:30.99,Default,,0,0,0,,Very well.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:43.42,0:07:44.67,Default,,0,0,0,,It's not like...
Dialogue: 0,0:07:47.00,0:07:49.13,Default,,0,0,0,,...I'm giving into...
Dialogue: 0,0:07:50.80,0:07:53.64,Default,,0,0,0,,...my baser emotions or anything...
Dialogue: 0,0:07:57.01,0:07:58.56,Default,,0,0,0,,Your Grace,
Dialogue: 0,0:07:58.56,0:07:59.89,Default,,0,0,0,,you're staring too hard.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:59.89,0:08:02.27,Default,,0,0,0,,I bet you were doing it on purpose!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:02.27,0:08:04.90,Default,,0,0,0,,Since I can't concentrate,\Nsave the cleaning for later and...
Dialogue: 0,0:08:04.90,0:08:08.28,Default,,0,0,0,,...come sit here and listen\Nto me play until I'm done.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:08.28,0:08:09.36,Default,,0,0,0,,All right.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:09.36,0:08:11.70,Default,,0,0,0,,Looks like I've got a front-row seat.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:11.70,0:08:13.82,Default,,0,0,0,,I wouldn't go so far as to say that.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:21.89,0:09:25.77,Default,,0,0,0,,It's a somber yet very beautiful song.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:25.77,0:09:27.69,Default,,0,0,0,,You know what?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:27.69,0:09:31.19,Default,,0,0,0,,You told me it sounded\Nlike a requiem earlier,
Dialogue: 0,0:09:31.19,0:09:35.28,Default,,0,0,0,,but I actually composed it\Nas a ballad for you.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:35.28,0:09:38.16,Default,,0,0,0,,I almost didn't ask you because\NI was too embarrassed to,
Dialogue: 0,0:09:38.16,0:09:42.49,Default,,0,0,0,,but after thinking about it some more,\NI really wanted you to hear it with me.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:47.21,0:09:50.00,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm feeling a bit tired,\Nso I think I'll take a nap.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:50.00,0:09:53.30,Default,,0,0,0,,Wake me up when dinner's ready.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:55.47,0:09:57.89,Default,,0,0,0,,I see. Very well...
Dialogue: 0,0:10:00.89,0:10:03.06,Default,,0,0,0,,...I shall kiss you good night.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:11.23,0:10:14.99,Default,,0,0,0,,I was only kidding. If you're going\Nto take a nap, please do it in bed.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:18.36,0:10:19.99,Default,,0,0,0,,Well, that sure woke me up!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:25.33,0:10:26.75,Default,,0,0,0,,May I please be excused?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:27.62,0:10:29.96,Default,,0,0,0,,You barely touched your plate.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:29.96,0:10:34.67,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm on a diet. Please give me\Na smaller helping tomorrow.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:34.67,0:10:39.51,Default,,0,0,0,,Hey, I'm starving. Don't we have\Nany apple crumble or something?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:39.51,0:10:41.60,Default,,0,0,0,,Didn't you say you were on a diet?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:41.60,0:10:43.56,Default,,0,0,0,,Come on, who cares?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:44.97,0:10:49.90,Default,,0,0,0,,Oh, that's right! I'm going out tomorrow,\Nso get the carriage ready.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:04.08,0:11:05.87,Default,,0,0,0,,It's so peaceful...
Dialogue: 0,0:11:05.87,0:11:07.58,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm making really good progress.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:07.58,0:11:09.58,Default,,0,0,0,,Looks like I'll get\Nmore done than I planned.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:11.50,0:11:14.88,Default,,0,0,0,,Oh, this mansion's as depressing as ever!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:14.88,0:11:17.30,Default,,0,0,0,,For being so run-down,\Nit's ridiculously huge!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:17.30,0:11:20.01,Default,,0,0,0,,The stress of just being here\Nwould make me break out in zits!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:20.01,0:11:21.26,Default,,0,0,0,,Definitely bad for the skin!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:21.26,0:11:24.39,Default,,0,0,0,,I don't know how he manages to live here!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:24.39,0:11:26.47,Default,,0,0,0,,Oh, there you are!\NI'm so sorry.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:26.47,0:11:29.31,Default,,0,0,0,,You're so unobtrusive I didn't\Neven notice you were there!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:29.31,0:11:32.35,Default,,0,0,0,,How long has it been, Dearest Brother?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:32.35,0:11:34.77,Default,,0,0,0,,Alice! Alice, come quick!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:36.98,0:11:38.44,Default,,0,0,0,,What's the matter?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:38.44,0:11:41.70,Default,,0,0,0,,You let her in the house again\Nwithout my permission, didn't you?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:41.70,0:11:44.28,Default,,0,0,0,,What a rude thing to say!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:44.28,0:11:48.00,Default,,0,0,0,,Lady Viola is Your Grace's\Nyounger sister, so...
Dialogue: 0,0:11:48.00,0:11:49.16,Default,,0,0,0,,That's right.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:49.16,0:11:53.96,Default,,0,0,0,,I have so graciously come to visit you,\Nso why don't you act happier?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:53.96,0:11:57.34,Default,,0,0,0,,It seems my dearest brother\Nwishes to speak with me,
Dialogue: 0,0:11:57.34,0:11:58.63,Default,,0,0,0,,so wait for me in the garden.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:58.63,0:11:59.88,Default,,0,0,0,,Yes, milady.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:59.88,0:12:01.59,Default,,0,0,0,,Nobody asked for this!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:05.97,0:12:08.77,Default,,0,0,0,,Mmm! This is great!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:08.77,0:12:11.73,Default,,0,0,0,,Tea is best served with\Nsweet crumpets, don't you think?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:11.73,0:12:14.86,Default,,0,0,0,,I don't think I could ever get my fill.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:14.86,0:12:16.86,Default,,0,0,0,,When are you planning on leaving today?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:16.86,0:12:18.36,Default,,0,0,0,,Oh, my God! How rude!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:18.36,0:12:20.65,Default,,0,0,0,,You don't have to tell me to go.\NI'm not staying long.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:22.28,0:12:26.74,Default,,0,0,0,,Mother will be angry with me\Nif she finds out I'm here.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:26.74,0:12:29.49,Default,,0,0,0,,Hey, can I have some more sweets?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:29.49,0:12:32.71,Default,,0,0,0,,And some Assam tea brewed\Nwith dried fruits, too!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:32.71,0:12:34.08,Default,,0,0,0,,Very well.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:34.08,0:12:35.92,Default,,0,0,0,,You've really got a lot of nerve!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:38.09,0:12:43.59,Default,,0,0,0,,My sister loves girly things like sweets\Nand talking about her love interests.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:43.59,0:12:48.76,Default,,0,0,0,,I suspect she drops by occasionally\Nfor a little change of pace.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:48.76,0:12:50.35,Default,,0,0,0,,But...
Dialogue: 0,0:12:50.35,0:12:52.06,Default,,0,0,0,,Hey, what are you looking at?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:52.06,0:12:56.52,Default,,0,0,0,,So, not only are you gloomy and unpopular,\Nyou're also into very young girls?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:56.52,0:12:59.65,Default,,0,0,0,,...I just can't handle her\N"charming" personality.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:59.65,0:13:02.11,Default,,0,0,0,,I brought you some sticky toffee pudding.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:02.11,0:13:03.90,Default,,0,0,0,,Wow! It looks delectable!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:03.90,0:13:05.99,Default,,0,0,0,,Sorry to put you to all this trouble.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:05.99,0:13:07.82,Default,,0,0,0,,It was no trouble at all.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:13.29,0:13:16.54,Default,,0,0,0,,Say, are you fond of that maid,\NDearest Brother?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:16.54,0:13:17.67,Default,,0,0,0,,Huh?!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:17.67,0:13:22.55,Default,,0,0,0,,Um... I'm fond of her...\NI mean, I adore her...
Dialogue: 0,0:13:22.55,0:13:24.42,Default,,0,0,0,,That was painful to watch.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:24.42,0:13:26.55,Default,,0,0,0,,Hey, that hurts!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:26.55,0:13:28.76,Default,,0,0,0,,Well, that explains it.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:28.76,0:13:30.76,Default,,0,0,0,,My dearest brother's in love.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:30.76,0:13:31.85,Default,,0,0,0,,Oh, well.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:31.85,0:13:35.69,Default,,0,0,0,,Little Miss Viola here will just have to\Nmake you popular, starting with that maid.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:35.69,0:13:38.27,Default,,0,0,0,,Using "The Viola Method of\NInstruction in the Art of Love."
Dialogue: 0,0:13:38.27,0:13:39.61,Default,,0,0,0,,The Viola Method?!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:39.61,0:13:43.82,Default,,0,0,0,,For example, everybody's got a\Ncomplex about something, right?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:43.82,0:13:47.32,Default,,0,0,0,,All you've got to do is\Njust hide whatever it is.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:47.32,0:13:50.58,Default,,0,0,0,,I have a round face,\Nso I hide the contours.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:50.58,0:13:52.79,Default,,0,0,0,,And it melts everyone's heart.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:52.79,0:13:54.45,Default,,0,0,0,,See? Look how adorable I am!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:54.45,0:13:56.50,Default,,0,0,0,,Sounds like you're tooting\Nyour own horn a bit too much.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:56.50,0:14:01.34,Default,,0,0,0,,In your case, Dearest Brother, you should\Nhide those dark circles under your eyes.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:01.34,0:14:03.21,Default,,0,0,0,,Y-You think?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:03.21,0:14:06.13,Default,,0,0,0,,--Like this?\N--Eww! Pull it down some more.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:06.13,0:14:07.26,Default,,0,0,0,,Is this far enough?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:07.26,0:14:09.14,Default,,0,0,0,,I feared as much. You just don't have\Nwhat it takes to be a ladies' man.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:09.14,0:14:10.68,Default,,0,0,0,,Try again in the next life!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:10.68,0:14:12.47,Default,,0,0,0,,You sure do give up easily!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:14.68,0:14:18.44,Default,,0,0,0,,After all this chit-chatting with\NDearest Brother, it's gotten so late.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:18.44,0:14:20.36,Default,,0,0,0,,Well, I was able to eat some tasty treats,
Dialogue: 0,0:14:20.36,0:14:23.53,Default,,0,0,0,,so I guess it wasn't a total waste\Nof time. I'll come again sometime.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:23.53,0:14:25.99,Default,,0,0,0,,Just stop dropping by unannounced, okay?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:25.99,0:14:26.95,Default,,0,0,0,,Or better yet...
Dialogue: 0,0:14:26.95,0:14:30.24,Default,,0,0,0,,Hurry up and break that curse so\Nyou can come back and live with us.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:31.16,0:14:33.08,Default,,0,0,0,,What are you blushing for?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:33.08,0:14:36.50,Default,,0,0,0,,If you think I said that out of concern\Nfor you, then you are sorely mistaken.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:36.50,0:14:38.37,Default,,0,0,0,,Who do you think you are, anyway?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:38.37,0:14:40.38,Default,,0,0,0,,You sure talk a lot of trash\Non your way out...
Dialogue: 0,0:14:41.75,0:14:44.00,Default,,0,0,0,,Hey, what's the big idea--
Dialogue: 0,0:14:44.00,0:14:45.67,Default,,0,0,0,,Rob?!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:45.67,0:14:49.26,Default,,0,0,0,,Well, if it isn't Lady Viola!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:49.26,0:14:53.10,Default,,0,0,0,,Oh, um... H-H-How long has it been?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:53.10,0:14:54.60,Default,,0,0,0,,It's been ages.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:54.60,0:14:58.39,Default,,0,0,0,,I see you made a special trip all\Nthe way out here just to pay us a visit.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:58.39,0:15:02.31,Default,,0,0,0,,I, um... wanted to see you, so...
Dialogue: 0,0:15:02.31,0:15:06.69,Default,,0,0,0,,Oh, you better be careful,\Nor your hair will get in your eyes.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:06.69,0:15:10.82,Default,,0,0,0,,Seems the Viola Method\Nis totally ineffective...
Dialogue: 0,0:15:10.82,0:15:13.37,Default,,0,0,0,,Who'd have thought she\Nwas into very old men...
Dialogue: 0,0:15:21.21,0:15:23.63,Default,,0,0,0,,"Hurry up and break that curse," huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:23.63,0:15:25.63,Default,,0,0,0,,That's easy for her to say...
Dialogue: 0,0:15:34.56,0:15:37.02,Default,,0,0,0,,Alice! Alice, come quick!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:38.89,0:15:40.85,Default,,0,0,0,,What's the matter, Your Grace?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:42.02,0:15:44.31,Default,,0,0,0,,Why, it's a cat!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:44.31,0:15:46.73,Default,,0,0,0,,It must've wandered\Nin here from the forest.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:46.73,0:15:49.44,Default,,0,0,0,,I can't go into the piano room\Nas long as it's here.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:49.44,0:15:51.82,Default,,0,0,0,,Hurry up and shoo it out of here!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:51.82,0:15:56.91,Default,,0,0,0,,You truly are adorable, Your Grace,\Nto make such a fuss over a single cat.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:56.91,0:15:59.54,Default,,0,0,0,,I-It's not like I'm scared\Nof it or anything!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:59.54,0:16:01.58,Default,,0,0,0,,It's just that it's hard to\Ntell what animals will do,
Dialogue: 0,0:16:01.58,0:16:04.29,Default,,0,0,0,,so I get worried I might\Naccidentally touch them.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:06.67,0:16:07.84,Default,,0,0,0,,Here, kitty!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:17.31,0:16:18.56,Default,,0,0,0,,Did you hear me?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:18.56,0:16:19.89,Default,,0,0,0,,Yes, I heard you.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:19.89,0:16:24.06,Default,,0,0,0,,But I just love animals.\NThey're so adorable.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:25.31,0:16:28.57,Default,,0,0,0,,It has a collar.\NCould it be a house cat?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:28.57,0:16:31.20,Default,,0,0,0,,Yeah, you're right. I wonder\Nif it ran away from home.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:31.20,0:16:33.49,Default,,0,0,0,,Let's set it loose in\Nthe forest right away.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:35.07,0:16:36.07,Default,,0,0,0,,Wait a...
Dialogue: 0,0:16:37.99,0:16:40.75,Default,,0,0,0,,Why is it after me?!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:40.75,0:16:42.75,Default,,0,0,0,,Try not to fall, now!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:42.75,0:16:44.21,Default,,0,0,0,,What?! Come save me!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:44.21,0:16:45.54,Default,,0,0,0,,Huh? Your Grace...
Dialogue: 0,0:16:45.54,0:16:47.59,Default,,0,0,0,,You mustn't crawl around\Non your hands and knees!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:47.59,0:16:49.17,Default,,0,0,0,,You think that looks like me?!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:49.17,0:16:51.76,Default,,0,0,0,,What you've got is worse\Nthan a case of aging eyes!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:51.76,0:16:55.68,Default,,0,0,0,,I picked you up without thinking, but--\NHey! This feels like a cat!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:55.68,0:16:56.85,Default,,0,0,0,,Oh, how cute!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:56.85,0:16:58.56,Default,,0,0,0,,Don't get all friendly with it!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:58.56,0:17:00.31,Default,,0,0,0,,Run free, kitty cat!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:00.31,0:17:02.23,Default,,0,0,0,,And after you went to\Nthe trouble of catching it!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:04.23,0:17:07.23,Default,,0,0,0,,Your Grace, the cat tore up\Nmy clothes with its claws...
Dialogue: 0,0:17:07.23,0:17:09.32,Default,,0,0,0,,Is that something you've\Ngot to tell me right now?!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:09.32,0:17:11.99,Default,,0,0,0,,But I can sew this up, and it'll be fine.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:11.99,0:17:14.15,Default,,0,0,0,,You don't have to widen\Nthe rips with your fingers!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:20.33,0:17:23.16,Default,,0,0,0,,So, it was reacting to my bolo tie.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:23.16,0:17:25.29,Default,,0,0,0,,What a pesky cat!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:25.29,0:17:29.21,Default,,0,0,0,,It certainly is a drawback not\Nknowing what animals will do.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:29.21,0:17:31.88,Default,,0,0,0,,That includes you, too.\NStop fiddling with those rips!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:33.42,0:17:34.55,Default,,0,0,0,,What's this?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:34.55,0:17:36.55,Default,,0,0,0,,Your Grace, there's a note.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:37.93,0:17:39.93,Default,,0,0,0,,Could this be the cat's name?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:39.93,0:17:40.93,Default,,0,0,0,,Beats me.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:42.81,0:17:45.73,Default,,0,0,0,,Please forgive me...
Dialogue: 0,0:17:45.73,0:17:47.27,Default,,0,0,0,,What does this mean?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:02.08,0:18:05.83,Default,,0,0,0,,So, you didn't run away.\NYou were abandoned. Just like me.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:07.46,0:18:10.42,Default,,0,0,0,,It's hard... being cast aside.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:18.76,0:18:22.97,Default,,0,0,0,,Well, it looks like the cat\Nalready found a new family.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:22.97,0:18:25.35,Default,,0,0,0,,Your tea is ready.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:25.35,0:18:29.86,Default,,0,0,0,,Please come in soon, Your Grace.\NYou wouldn't want to catch a cold.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:29.86,0:18:31.94,Default,,0,0,0,,All right, I'm coming.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:48.87,0:18:52.50,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}In the gloom of the forest{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:18:52.50,0:18:56.80,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}I stand where I was abandoned{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:18:56.80,0:19:00.51,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}No one will hear{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:19:00.51,0:19:04.64,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}My feeble, heart-rending cry{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:19:04.64,0:19:08.81,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}I want to go back{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:19:08.81,0:19:12.81,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}But I can never go back{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:19:12.81,0:19:20.66,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}To that warm and loving place{\i0}\N{\i1}that I miss so much{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:19:21.20,0:19:24.62,Default,,0,0,0,,So, this is where you've been, Your Grace.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:24.62,0:19:27.33,Default,,0,0,0,,Your dinner is ready.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:27.33,0:19:30.21,Default,,0,0,0,,What have you been doing?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:30.21,0:19:34.80,Default,,0,0,0,,The moon is so beautiful, so I was\Njust standing here thinking.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:34.80,0:19:40.13,Default,,0,0,0,,I don't come in here much, but the view\Nfrom this ballroom certainly is lovely.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:40.13,0:19:42.39,Default,,0,0,0,,No one comes in here much\Nbecause there's no reason to.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:42.39,0:19:44.30,Default,,0,0,0,,Rob once told me that a long time ago,
Dialogue: 0,0:19:44.30,0:19:48.06,Default,,0,0,0,,my grandfather couldn't\Ndance to save his life,
Dialogue: 0,0:19:48.06,0:19:51.27,Default,,0,0,0,,so he used to come here\Nlate at night to practice.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:51.27,0:19:55.82,Default,,0,0,0,,And apparently, his dance partner\Nat the time was your mother.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:59.65,0:20:01.24,Default,,0,0,0,,Don't you find that interesting?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:01.24,0:20:06.79,Default,,0,0,0,,My grandfather and your mother\Ndanced in this very room.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:06.79,0:20:09.58,Default,,0,0,0,,I feel like it was fate\Nthat brought us here.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:09.58,0:20:12.71,Default,,0,0,0,,It certainly could be an act of fate.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:16.17,0:20:20.47,Default,,0,0,0,,S-Shall we give it a try ourselves?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:20.47,0:20:24.89,Default,,0,0,0,,I can't touch you, but we can coordinate\Nour movements to approximate dancing.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:24.89,0:20:26.97,Default,,0,0,0,,I must decline.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:26.97,0:20:31.23,Default,,0,0,0,,Oh, I see... I thought it\Nwould be fun, but...
Dialogue: 0,0:20:31.23,0:20:34.02,Default,,0,0,0,,Unless you ask me properly,\NI must decline.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:39.65,0:20:44.28,Default,,0,0,0,,May I... have this dance?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:46.62,0:20:47.95,Default,,0,0,0,,I'd be delighted.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:04.34,0:21:07.60,Default,,0,0,0,,Aren't you a little too close?\NBe careful not to touch me.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:07.60,0:21:12.98,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm used to it. It's just...\NI haven't danced much at all.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:12.98,0:21:15.23,Default,,0,0,0,,Neither have I.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:15.23,0:21:18.02,Default,,0,0,0,,It's more difficult than I imagined.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:20.19,0:21:22.99,Default,,0,0,0,,But... it's delightful.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:18.14,0:23:21.19,Default,,0,0,0,,Alice, can I ask you something?
Dialogue: 0,0:23:21.19,0:23:22.36,Default,,0,0,0,,Certainly.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:22.36,0:23:25.86,Default,,0,0,0,,What do you think of me?
Dialogue: 0,0:23:25.86,0:23:27.19,Default,,0,0,0,,You're an important person.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:27.19,0:23:30.70,Default,,0,0,0,,No, not in the sense of\Na master and his servant...
Dialogue: 0,0:23:30.70,0:23:35.08,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm asking you what you\Nthink of me as a man.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:35.08,0:23:37.79,Default,,0,0,0,,Well, of course I like you, Your Grace.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:37.79,0:23:39.00,Default,,0,0,0,,Really?!
Dialogue: 0,0:23:39.00,0:23:39.87,Default,,0,0,0,,Why, yes.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:39.87,0:23:44.29,Default,,0,0,0,,I like you. I love you. I adore you. I\Nonly have eyes for you, Your Grace.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:44.29,0:23:45.84,Default,,0,0,0,,All right, that's enough!
Dialogue: 0,0:23:45.84,0:23:48.22,Default,,0,0,0,,There aren't enough words\Nto express the way I feel.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:49.13,0:23:52.30,Default,,0,0,0,,I never would've thought you'd say that.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:52.30,0:23:54.43,Default,,0,0,0,,I think I'll have my dinner now.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:54.43,0:23:56.81,Default,,0,0,0,,Very well, Your Grace.
Dialogue: 0,0:24:06.82,0:24:09.99,Default,,0,0,0,,"The Duke and the Meteor\NShower During the Full Moon."
